      "authorAssociation": "MEMBER",
      "body": "Dear all, \n\nThe proposal has been made to obsolete GO:0003400 regulation of COPII vesicle coating.\n\n* The reason for obsoletion is that the data from the paper for which the term was requested can be accurately described using GO:0048208 COPII vesicle coating.\n\nExperimental annotations\nSGD 8\nUniProt 3\n\nThere is one UniRule/UniProtKW mapping.\n\nAnnotations can be viewed here: https://github.com/geneontology/go-annotation/issues/6389.\n\nThis term is being replaced by GO:0048208 COPII vesicle coating.\n\nAny comments can be  added to the issue: https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31945\n\nThanks, ",
